          <h2 class="section-headline" id="origin-headline">
            30 years in travel.<br>
            Hit the wall.<br>
            <em>Started building tech.</em>
          </h2>

          <div class="origin-story">
            <p>
              REAL TEAM started as a family travel agency in 1994. Our parents ran group trips — school ski trips,
              youth sport tournaments, thousands of participants over three decades. When we started running FRESH,
              our international sport camp, we managed 200+ athletes from 42 countries across five sold-out editions. All on spreadsheets and email chains.
            </p>
            <p>
              The process worked — until it didn't scale. Too many names, too many variable dates, too many
              back-and-forth emails with the hotel. We looked for existing solutions. Nothing fit.
              So we built GroupFlow. Thanks to AI we can build faster and more professionally — but it's 30 years
              of organizing group travel that tells us what to build.
            </p>
          </div>

          <a href="https://realteamsport.de" class="origin-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            See the full story at realteamsport.de
