          <h3 class="groupflow-audience">Your front desk knows this</h3>
          <p class="groupflow-problem-text">
            A group booking request arrives. You send the rooming list template.
            Wait for it back. Re-enter 40 names manually. The organizer sends corrections.
            Re-enter again. Someone changes their dates. Another email. Export to the PMS somehow.
            Repeat for every group, every season.
          </p>

          <div>
